<title>BRIGHTNESS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuhin Isu Nangmah kawmah,
 Na Sapchuom laka um dingin
 Thutiem ah nau ka hun pieu hi,
 Pawm inla, Na Thagau vukin.

[V2]
 2. &quot;Naupang neuhaw chu ka kawmah,
 A hung phal un la, haw kiu in,&quot;
 Zie khawvel a Na tih sek kha,
 Ka kipak un, ka ngaisang ui.

[V3]
 3. Ma a Pathien ging Hani khan,
 Nasepna'n a cha chuh a piei;
 Tuhin le kipakin ka pieu,
 Samuel tawbang hung hi hen.

[V4]
 4. Loisi leh Eunik-mi phate khan,
 Naupang cha a hih lai apat;
 Timothe a sinsak bang un,
 Bible thu hun sinsak u hen.

[V5]
 5. Zie leisiet go thilpha pen hi,
 Nangmah kawmah ka hun pieu hi;
 Changin, vawpin kumkhuon vengin,
 Van Sapchuom lak ale pawmin.</lyrics>
</song>